WEBVTT

00:00.909 --> 00:02.809
<i>Previously on Kyle XY...</i>

00:02.844 --> 00:05.336
- Kyle?
- Be careful, even in our backyard.

00:05.381 --> 00:09.147
We have bigger problems.
Jessi starts back at school today.

00:09.185 --> 00:10.517
I sort of levitated.

00:10.554 --> 00:12.215
- Show me how.
- I will.

00:12.255 --> 00:15.747
- She's the one who attacked me.
- I know Lori will never forgive me.

00:15.792 --> 00:17.124
Earn forgiveness.

00:17.228 --> 00:19.560
<i>- She Could Be You.
- What?</i>

00:19.597 --> 00:22.294
The two of you used to play
that song all the time.

00:22.334 --> 00:24.461
D4.

00:24.503 --> 00:25.902
It's not there.

00:25.938 --> 00:28.669
It's a Latnok ring.
All the members received rings.

00:28.708 --> 00:30.369
A way of identifying one another.

00:30.443 --> 00:32.171
- Then you're Latnok?
- Yes.

00:32.212 --> 00:34.704
I got accepted into
a music program in New York.

00:34.748 --> 00:36.841
- I leave in two days.
- Two days?

00:36.884 --> 00:38.351
I miss this.

00:39.720 --> 00:40.983
I miss you.

00:41.022 --> 00:44.321
I didn't want to go back
to how I was before.

00:44.359 --> 00:46.088
How were you before?

00:46.127 --> 00:48.028
Invisible.

00:48.097 --> 00:51.965
I'll call and text and e-mail.
I'm gonna come back to you.

00:52.034 --> 00:54.299
- You promise?
- Promise.

